<item>
            <title>[HBASE-6] Opening then closing a scanner delays the effects of a delete</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-6</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I stumbled across the following odd behavior: When I open, then close a scanner on&lt;br/&gt;
a table, then delete a row in the table, the delete does not work&lt;br/&gt;
(i.e., I can still get the row).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
