                            <comment id="12556790" author="clint.morgan" created="Tue, 8 Jan 2008 01:01:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The test does the following.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Insert a row.&lt;br/&gt;
Read the row. &lt;br/&gt;
Open and the close a scanner.&lt;br/&gt;
Delete the row.&lt;br/&gt;
Try and read the row (FAILURE, the row is still there)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If I don&apos;t have the scanner in here, then everything works as&lt;br/&gt;
expected.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
